each 
each cell is led by a political officer who conducts 
teachins and is responsible for a specific task such as 
propaganda or communications he said 
as in the communist underground members of one cell usually 
know only one member of any other cell this enables cells to 
maintain contact without fear that a single arrest could compromise 
an entire group he said 
sources say you sponsors marxiststyle political discussions 
among combat units and is trying to establish support groups 
among civilians to broaden its base 
you statements are replete with the same references to 
american imperialism and the aquino puppet regime as those 
of the communists 
a considerable number of young military officers have come to 
realize that their supreme loyalty is to uphold the dignity 
freedom and social justice that the filipino people rightfully 
deserve you said in a recent statement 
we vow cory will not finish her term as an illegitimate 
