and focuses on lobbying legislation and other political activity 
susan smith the organizations associate legislative director 
said the group is working uphill to counter the media hype that 
the proabortion movement creates 
ten 20 years down the road i expect well be a little further 
along than we are now smith said 
one workshop at the convention was titled working a biased 
media to the advantage of the movement 
