compromised by up to 15 different security leaks 
gen manuel antonio noriega knew at 10 pm the night before the 
invasion that there was a chance the united states would attack 
newsweek said 
however noriega dismissed the reports newsweek said 
the leaks came from girlfriends of us soldiers in panama 
