a shootout while on the run from a double murder he committed in 
columbia sc 
arkansas would become the 14th state to carry out an execution 
and swindler the 130th inmate put to death since the us supreme 
court in 1976 let states resume use of capital punishment 
arkansas plans another execution on june 25 ronald gene simmons 
is to die by injection for the 1987 killings of 16 people 
including 14 family members 
because swindler was sentenced before arkansas changed its 
