spokesman raja muzzafar 
khans organization wants the former princely state of kashmir 
now split between india and pakistan to be reunited and granted 
independence clashes during the 6monthold uprising mostly in 
india have left more than 550 people dead 
mondays announcement by the secessionists came shortly before 
