cranbury njbased art supply firm were on the nrdc list of 
consumer products containing 111 
godfrey chambers technical services manager for grumbacher 
said the four products damar varnish myston retouch varnish and 
tuffilm fixative are manufactured by a supplier and purchased by 
grumbacher for resale 
the person we purchase it from is continuing research in this 
matter to try and eliminate it chambers said he said the 
company has already removed 111 from some of its other aerosols 
