fainted as witnesses described their illegal abortions and 
selfinduced miscarriages 
aides who orchestrate these hearings say politicians find it 
difficult to be argumentative or ideological when a victim is 
sitting in front of them 
if a woman says she thwarted the law and risked her health to 
get an illegal abortion that decisionmaking process is 
something thats hard to secondguess said kelly signs an aide 
to sen howard metzenbaum dohio 
