carreras did not lose religious faith while he was so sick i 
think my faith grew after that i have to be honest 
at the beginning after you recover you think your life is 
going to change dramatically slowly slowly slowly you go back 
to the same mistakes what was your plan for a fantastic new life 
you keep your word for only 20 percent 
but this 20 percent is a big change in many things you 
probably see things from a more relaxing quiet peaceful way you 
