but you didnt notice it maybe 
after such an extreme moment of your life you become more 
mature for the important things in life what is wonderful is that 
after such a bad period many of the conclusions are very positive 
so that if life was wonderful before now it is 100 percent 
wonderful in so many aspects i think im richer inside 
