we have our own buses custom built for us with beds and tvs and 
bathrooms and microwaves we buy microwave pizzas and premade 
stuff 
everywhere we go girls are out in front we have jealous 
boyfriends pull up in front of our houses at 3 in the morning 
screaming at the top of their lungs we learn to live with it the 
good things far outweigh the bad things 
when the first album didnt sell hugely jonathan said our 
manager starr was telling us we have to wait our turn as long as 
we keep working hard and doing the best we can do our dreams will 
come true hes always positive about everything 
during the twoweek vacation before going to europe wahlberg 
