four brothers older than himself 
during those two weeks jonathan worked in his yard until 4 am 
ive got those nightowl eyes he says i was out there 
putting in a pond planting bushes getting the yard ready me and 
jordan just bought a house for our family they have two sisters 
and two more brothers at home theyre not jealous they know god 
carved out my life to do what im doing and they have their special 
place in life to fulfill their dreams 
we all still live with our families we want to have our 
